{
  "stem": "1857.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 379.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then my father had a very different office, who was a importer of Italian accordions.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I-- I used to play a little bit the accordion.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So-- and the firm was taken over by a Ukrainian-- what they call [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[SPEAKING GERMAN] in German is man of confidence for the German-- German government.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They put somebody like this in confidence to-- to-- to do conduct business and take it out of the Jewish hands.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this man was put in, this Ukrainian, who was a very sort of sympathetic man, quite intelligent.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He used to be a-- a editor of a Ukrainian newspaper in eastern Poland.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he had a son my age who served in the Sonderdienst, which was a special unit of the German Army.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he got to like me, and we-- He took me around Krakow.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I was taking off my armband while walked with him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I worked for them--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was actually a packing and shipping clerk at that place.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that work I enjoyed, because whenever I had free time, I could tinker around on the accordion.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] That finally ended when we were required to have, second half of 1940-- by the end of 1940, they were giving out what they called Kennkarte.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Kennkarte was an identification that whoever had identification could remain in city of Krakow.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "By January of 1941, they started building the ghetto on the outskirts of Krakow, in-- in the outskirts called Podgorze, which was on the other side of the Vistula River.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And whoever had a Kennkarte could remain in Krakow.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Whoever did not get a Kennkarte had to leave Krakow, and they didn't care where.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we did not receive the Kennkarte.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
